Invocation Name: u. c. f. s. healthcare
des: UCFS Healthcare is on a mission to improve the health of our community and to redefine well-being. Through comprehensive, quality healthcare services at locations throughout eastern Connecticut, we meet the needs of clients at every stage of life. Dedicated to making healthcare more convenient, we have developed this app to instantly answer common questions about our services, locations, policies, and resources. You can ask your smart speaker a full range of questions about our providers, the insurance we accept and what to expect on your first appointment. This app consistently evolves to address any gaps in information delivery not initially considered at launch. For further information please visit ucfshealthcare.org.
